steps.instruction:
Found from [Publix Aprons](https://ww4.publix.com/recipes-planning/aprons-recipes/pineapple-mojito-sangria)

1. Muddle lime slices, mint leaves, and sugar in large pitcher.
2. Stir in pineapple, wine, pineapple juice, and rum. Cover and chill 2–3 hours.
3. Stir in lemon-lime soda just before serving over ice. Garnish with a pineapple wedge and mint leaves.
